your whole business plan.

00:08:27,307 --> 00:08:29,576
There you go.
You get a guy that doesn't
eat your product

00:08:29,576 --> 00:08:32,712
to tell you what to do.
And a mentor who's done it
every step of the way

00:08:32,712 --> 00:08:34,014
and who's gonna guide you.

00:08:34,014 --> 00:08:36,249
You would be a fool not to walk
out with one of these offers.

00:08:36,249 --> 00:08:39,786
Which Shark or Sharks
do you want to go with?

00:08:39,786 --> 00:08:41,354
Wong: Gosh.

00:08:41,354 --> 00:08:45,992
I mean, I would be honored
to officiate this wedding.

00:08:45,992 --> 00:08:48,395
The valuation is a little rich.

00:08:48,395 --> 00:08:55,702
I'm wondering if we could bring
you two in at 300K for 15%.

00:08:55,702 --> 00:08:58,972
300K for 15%?

00:08:58,972 --> 00:09:01,341
O'Leary:
That's not crazy.

00:09:02,942 --> 00:09:04,744
I would do that.

00:09:04,744 --> 00:09:06,579
You've got a deal.
Done.

00:09:06,579 --> 00:09:08,281
‐Congratulations.
‐Whoo!

00:09:08,281 --> 00:09:11,251
I would hug you, but
we'd have to quarantine
for two more weeks.

00:09:11,251 --> 00:09:13,987
Greiner: Good job.
Phil, we're really excited
to work with you.

00:09:13,987 --> 00:09:15,989
We are very excited about you.
We are going to crush it.

00:09:15,989 --> 00:09:17,590
Wong: Thank you.
Crush it.

00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:18,124
I'm so excited.

00:09:18,124 --> 00:09:19,959
If we don't create
a whole new category

00:09:19,959 --> 00:09:23,063
and dominate that category,
I'll be really disappointed.

00:09:23,063 --> 00:09:24,831
We'll make it happen.
Thank you, guys.

00:09:24,831 --> 00:09:28,735
‐Phil, congratulations.
‐Yeah, congrats.

00:09:28,735 --> 00:09:31,371
Oh, my gosh.

00:09:32,939 --> 00:09:35,375
[ Exhales sharply ]

00:09:36,776 --> 00:09:38,078
Oh.

00:09:38,078 --> 00:09:42,015
Wow, that was not what
I was expecting to happen.

00:09:42,015 --> 00:09:44,417
So we came out
with both Daniel and Mark.

00:09:44,417 --> 00:09:48,254
I mean, both of those are like
two huge business idols for me.

00:09:48,254 --> 00:09:51,157
And so I'm kind of fanboy‐ing
right now.

00:09:51,157 --> 00:09:55,462
It's gonna be a game changer for
our business, that's for sure.

