5,500 Sleep Pods.

00:10:20,086 --> 00:10:22,722
The night we aired,
something magical happened.

00:10:22,722 --> 00:10:24,891
We sold over $2 million
in sales,

00:10:24,891 --> 00:10:26,993
well over
25,000 Sleep Pods.

00:10:26,993 --> 00:10:28,962
Kupper:
Our focus quickly shifted to,

00:10:28,962 --> 00:10:31,764
"How are we going to be able
