our manufacturer
was able to make

00:10:34,134 --> 00:10:36,636
about 200 to 300 units
per week.

00:10:36,636 --> 00:10:37,837
We were able
to scale production

00:10:37,837 --> 00:10:39,873
to well over
10,000 units a week.

00:10:39,873 --> 00:10:41,107
In just three
short months,

00:10:41,107 --> 00:10:44,010
We've done over
$4.1 million in sales

00:10:44,010 --> 00:10:47,046
and have sold
over 44,000 Sleep Pods.

00:10:47,046 --> 00:10:49,215
Sleep is everything
to everybody.

00:10:49,215 --> 00:10:52,018
If you can't sleep,
then everything else craters.

00:10:52,018 --> 00:10:54,020
Especially during
these stressful times.

00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:55,989
Greiner: The future
for this business is bright.

